{"tid":1366895,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［回帶］其實生理鹽水唔係神仙水，同普通水冇乜分別。","createTime":"2019-07-26T05:54:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T13:27:53.000Z","uid":32536,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ba3e795c90c9b898f72e126d8ce6deb218024741","tid":1366895,"uid":32536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T05:54:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">推返上黎 物資不足 寧願多蒸餾水好過個個買鹽水</span><br />\n<br />\n以下係回帶：<br />\n<br />\n（醫生/ 護士/ 急救員可以上一頁，或者我有講錯嘅可以指正我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n首先，沖皮膚係唔撚駛特別用生理鹽水！講講咩係生理鹽水，其實只係0.9%濃度嘅鹽水（食鹽）<br />\n<br />\n佢冇殺菌作用<br />\n比較水嚟講，佢冇更強嘅溶解同沖洗催淚氣體作用<br />\n<br />\n佢只係起沖洗眼睛，鼻腔會&ldquo;舒服&rdquo;啲，沖洗傷口會造成少啲破壞。（細胞/ 紅血球起純水會爆）<br />\n<br />\n所以大家要珍惜生理鹽水，留返俾更有需要嘅人（例如見血嘅人）。<span style=\"color: red;\">附近冇鹽水嘅，唔好等啦，求其用支樽裝水啦屌！</span>好多嘅場合其實唔需要咁身嬌肉貴用生理鹽水。"},{"pid":"214e30b0019df79274314e60862eef046e533562","tid":1366895,"uid":32536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T05:55:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0e276af469cf43714167b6e6f79a8749a156954","tid":1366895,"uid":32536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T05:56:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c36f69fdc5cb3a5ba1b6706c71f5028eee694530","tid":1366895,"uid":32536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T05:56:43.000Z",